experiment NWIND
instrument TRO
start 2017 11 13 1600
end 2017 11 13 1800
status R
description Joint observation using EISCAT radars and FPI
contact Lei Cai
email lei.cai@oulu.fi
operator Ilkka Virtanen
submitter Lei Cai
resources FI(2)
notes
The ion-neutral coupling will be studied in the vicinity of auroral structures.
Substorm events are preferred. Electric field will be estimated using the
UHF/CP2. Simultaneously, thermospheric winds will be measured by
the FPI (Nagoya University) at TRO. 
